title: Fallout.4.Wasteland.Workshop.DLC.Incl.Beta.Update.v1.5.147
description:
Install instructions:
- Copy the Data folder to your main game dir
- Play

Optional: You need to have beta update v1.5.141 installed if you want to apply the beta update in this torrent!
- Go to the update folder and run Setup.exe to apply the new beta update.
- Copy over the contents in the Crack folder
- Play

PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS! :)
If you like this game, support the developers and BUY IT!
